        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice the <span class=\"text-highlight\"><strong>red</strong></span> <strong>chilli<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> into rounds</p>\n<p>Slice the <strong>rested steaks</strong> finely</p>\n<p>Stir any of the <strong>resting juices</strong> through the <strong>teriyaki sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
